task.summary: Fixed 'NEB cannot run when sharing the same calculator'
Removed dependency between serial and parallel version of AI-NEB.
Restart from the MEP of previous iteration implemented.
Parallel NEB with dynamic process management implemented.
Revised parallel version of AI-NEB and added INSTALL notes.
CI-NEB now starts with a new NEB instance.
Added IDPP interpolation for generating training data set.
